data.title: 1938) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: MICHAEL BAUER  Michael Bauer, 71, a resident of Elkhart since 1910, died at 6:30 Tuesday evening of last week at his home, 403 West Washington street, Elkhart.  He had been ill since December 11 with paralysis.  Mr. Bauer was born on a farm near Wakarusa, May 12, 1866, the son of Mr. and Mrs. Christian Bauer  Surviving...
